Method Detail

create

@RequestMapping(value="{username}/{shiftId}",
                method=POST,
                consumes="application/json",
                produces="application/json")
@ResponseBody
@PreAuthorize(value="hasRole(\'employer\')")
public PlannedShift create(@RequestBody
                                                                    Date date,
                                                                    @PathVariable
                                                                    String username,
                                                                    @PathVariable
                                                                    Long shiftId)
Handles POST requests to "plannedshifts/username/shiftId". Gets date as a parameter from request and creates a new planned shift for username/shift/date combination.

Parameters:
date - the date from request
username - username from path
shiftId - shift id from path
Returns:
the saved planned shift

list

@RequestMapping(value="",
                method=GET,
                produces="application/json")
@ResponseBody
@PreAuthorize(value="permitAll")
public List<PlannedShift> list()
Handles GET requests to "wss/plannedshifts". Responds with the current week's planned shift list.

Returns:
list of current week's planned shifts

listByWeek

@RequestMapping(value="{year}/{weekNumber}",
                method=GET,
                produces="application/json")
@ResponseBody
@PreAuthorize(value="permitAll")
public List<PlannedShift> listByWeek(@PathVariable
                                                                              int year,
                                                                              @PathVariable
                                                                              int weekNumber)
Handles GET requests to "plannedshifts/year/weeknumber". Responds with the week's planned shift list.

Parameters:
year - requested year from path
weekNumber - requested week number from path
Returns:
list of planned shifts for that week

delete

                method=DELETE)
@ResponseBody
@PreAuthorize(value="hasRole(\'employer\')")
public void delete(@PathVariable
                                                            Long plannedShiftId)
Handles DELETE requests to "plannedshifts/id". Deletes the shift that has the id.

Parameters:
plannedShiftId - shift id from path

weekInfo

@RequestMapping(value="weekinfo",
                method=GET,
                produces="application/json")
@ResponseBody
@PreAuthorize(value="permitAll")
public Week weekInfo()
Handles GET requests to plannedshifts/weekinfo. Responds with the info of the current week (dates for each day and year/week number).

Returns:
the current week info
